intent.user_query: Which product brands have the highest number of open service tickets (status is not 'Resolved')?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.Brand, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS OpenTicketCount FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID WHERE st.Status <> 'Resolved' GROUP BY p.Brand ORDER BY OpenTicketCount DESC;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.Brand, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS OpenTicketCount FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID WHERE st.Status <> 'Resolved' GROUP BY p.Brand ORDER BY OpenTicketCount DESC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
